Dee Hartford https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dee_Hartford 0 Dee Hartford (born Donna Higgins, April 21, 1928) is a retired American television actress. She was married to Howard Hawks from 1953-59. Her sister was actress Eden Hartford. Dee_Hartford ( born Donna_Higgins , April_21_,_1928 ) is a_retired_American_television_actress . She was_married to Howard_Hawks from 1953-59 .
